
root@1cf92638093f:/home/gv/gpuverify/InvariantGenerationBenchmarks# for line in $(find . -type f  -name '*.cl' -o -name '*.cu'); do echo  ""; echo "" ; echo ""; echo $line ; param=`head -n2  $line | tail -1 | cut -c 3-` ; all_param=" --keep-temps --verbose --infer-info --time --timeout=0  --debug  --boogie-opt=/trace --solver=z3  $param" ; echo ${all_param}  ;  { time timeout 10s  gpuverify $all_param $line  ; } 2>&1 ;  echo $line ; done
